| Cold constitution | Pao Jiang + Rou Gui | Warm middle jiao |
| Poor appetite | Sha Ren + Chen Pi | Promote appetite, move qi |

### Classical Variations
- **Liu Jun Zi Tang**: + Chen Pi + Ban Xia for phlegm-dampness
- **Xiang Sha Liu Jun Zi Tang**: + Chen Pi + Ban Xia + Sha Ren + Mu Xiang for qi stagnation
- **Bu Zhong Yi Qi Tang**: + Huang Qi + Dang Gui + Sheng Ma + Chai Hu for qi sinking

### Modern Modifications
- For immune support: Add Huang Qi and Ling Zhi
- For children: Reduce Ren Shen, add Shan Yao and Yi Yi Ren
- For elderly: Add Dang Gui and He Shou Wu for blood support

